This file lists the amount of RAM used by the tiny sphincs package

Parameter Set           CTX size  Keygen size  Sig size  Ver size

Legend:
Parameter Set - the Sphincs+ parameter set being tested.  Each test used a minimal tune.h to enable the named parameter set
CTX size - the size of the ts_context structure used to track Sphincs+ state while streaming.  This is included in the RAM usage for Sig size and Ver size
Keygen size - the amount of RAM used for key generation
Sig size - the amount of RAM used for signature generation
Ver size - the amount of RAM used for signature verification
